{"id": "art-17", "label": "Art. 17", "title": "Art. 17", "slug": "art-17", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 17 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Anterior\nîncheierii sau modific&#259;rii contractului individual de munc&#259;,\nangajatorul are obliga&#355;ia de a informa persoana selectat&#259; în vederea\nangaj&#259;rii ori, dup&#259; caz, salariatul, cu privire la clauzele\nesen&#355;iale pe care inten&#355;ioneaz&#259; s&#259; le înscrie în contract\nsau s&#259; le modifice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Obliga&#355;ia de informare a\npersoanei selectate în vederea angaj&#259;rii sau a salariatului se\nconsider&#259; îndeplinit&#259; de c&#259;tre angajator la momentul\nsemn&#259;rii contractului individual de munc&#259; sau a actului\nadi&#355;ional, dup&#259; caz.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Persoana selectat&#259; în vederea angaj&#259;rii ori salariatul,\ndup&#259; caz, va fi informat&#259; cu privire la cel pu&#355;in\nurm&#259;toarele elemente:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)identitatea\np&#259;r&#355;ilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1916620335\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1379\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1916620335\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)locul de munc&#259; sau, în lipsa unui loc de munc&#259;\nfix, posibilitatea ca salariatul s&#259; î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oare\nactivitatea în locuri de munc&#259; diferite, precum &#351;i dac&#259;\ndeplasarea între acestea este asigurat&#259; sau decontat&#259; de c&#259;tre\nangajator, dup&#259; caz;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)sediul\nsau, dup&#259; caz, domiciliul angajatorului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)func&#355;ia/ocupa&#355;ia\nconform specifica&#355;iei Clasific&#259;rii ocupa&#355;iilor din România sau\naltor acte normative, precum &#351;i fi&#351;a postului, cu specificarea\natribu&#355;iilor postului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>e)criteriile\nde evaluare a activit&#259;&#355;ii profesionale a salariatului aplicabile la\nnivelul angajatorului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>f)riscurile\nspecifice postului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>g)data\nde la care contractul urmeaz&#259; s&#259; î&#351;i produc&#259; efectele;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>h)în\ncazul unui contract de munc&#259; pe durat&#259; determinat&#259; sau al unui\ncontract de munc&#259; temporar&#259;, durata acestora;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>i)durata\nconcediului de odihn&#259; la care salariatul are dreptul;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>j)condi&#355;iile\nde acordare a preavizului de c&#259;tre p&#259;r&#355;ile contractante &#351;i\ndurata acestuia;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_5509205\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1378\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_5509205\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>k)salariul de baz&#259;, alte elemente constitutive ale\nveniturilor salariale, eviden&#355;iate separat, periodicitatea\npl&#259;&#355;ii salariului la care salariatul are dreptul &#351;i metoda de\nplat&#259;;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_279659520\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1377\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_279659520\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>l)durata normal&#259; a muncii, exprimat&#259; în ore/zi\n&#351;i/sau ore/s&#259;pt&#259;mân&#259;, condi&#355;iile de efectuare &#351;i\nde compensare sau de plat&#259; a orelor suplimentare, precum &#351;i,\ndac&#259; este cazul, modalit&#259;&#355;ile de organizare a muncii în\nschimburi;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>m)indicarea\ncontractului colectiv de munc&#259; ce reglementeaz&#259; condi&#355;iile de\nmunc&#259; ale salariatului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_985054658\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1376\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_985054658\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>n)durata &#351;i condi&#355;iile perioadei de prob&#259;,\ndac&#259; exist&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1138004122\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1375\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1138004122\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>o)procedurile privind utilizarea semn&#259;turii\nelectronice, semn&#259;turii electronice avansate &#351;i semn&#259;turii\nelectronice calificate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_605572473\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1374\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_605572473\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>p)dreptul &#351;i condi&#355;iile privind formarea\nprofesional&#259; oferit&#259; de angajator;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_382990180\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1373\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_382990180\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>q)suportarea de c&#259;tre angajator a asigur&#259;rii\nmedicale private, a contribu&#355;iilor suplimentare la pensia facultativ&#259;\nsau la pensia ocupa&#355;ional&#259; a salariatului, în condi&#355;iile legii,\nprecum &#351;i acordarea, din ini&#355;iativa angajatorului, a oric&#259;ror\nalte drepturi, atunci când acestea constituie avantaje în bani acordate sau\npl&#259;tite de angajator salariatului ca urmare a activit&#259;&#355;ii\nprofesionale a acestuia, dup&#259; caz.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_335712203\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1372\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_335712203\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Elementele din informarea prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin.\n(3) trebuie s&#259; se reg&#259;seasc&#259; &#351;i în con&#355;inutul\ncontractului individual de munc&#259;, cu excep&#355;ia informa&#355;iilor\nprev&#259;zute la lit. m), o) &#351;i p).</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1801361522\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1371\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1801361522\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Orice modificare a unuia dintre elementele\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (3) în timpul execut&#259;rii contractului individual\nde munc&#259; impune încheierea unui act adi&#355;ional la contract, anterior\nproducerii modific&#259;rii, cu excep&#355;ia situa&#355;iilor în care o\nasemenea modificare este prev&#259;zut&#259; în mod expres de lege sau în\ncontractul colectiv de munc&#259; aplicabil.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1760292842\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1370\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1760292842\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)La negocierea, încheierea sau modificarea contractului\nindividual de munc&#259; ori pe durata concilierii unui conflict individual de\nmunc&#259;, oricare dintre p&#259;r&#355;i poate fi asistat&#259; de c&#259;tre\nun consultant extern specializat în legisla&#355;ia muncii sau de c&#259;tre un\nreprezentant al sindicatului al c&#259;rui membru este, conform propriei\nop&#355;iuni, cu respectarea prevederilor alin. (7).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1722249107\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1369\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1722249107\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Cu privire la informa&#355;iile furnizate, prealabil\nîncheierii contractului individual de munc&#259; sau pe parcursul\nexecut&#259;rii acestuia, inclusiv pe durata concilierii, între p&#259;r&#355;i\npoate interveni un contract de confiden&#355;ialitate.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_888505698\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1368\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_888505698\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Inspec&#355;ia Muncii pune la dispozi&#355;ia\nangaja&#355;ilor &#351;i a angajatorilor modelul-cadru al contractului\nindividual de munc&#259;, stabilit prin ordin al ministrului muncii &#351;i\nsolidarit&#259;&#355;ii sociale, prin publicarea pe site-ul institu&#355;iei.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_927211978\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1367\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_927211978\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Toate informa&#355;iile men&#355;ionate la art. 17 alin.\n(3) vor fi cuprinse în modelul-cadru al contractului individual de munc&#259;\nprev&#259;zut la alin. (8).</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}